\">To:升天南<br />\n<br />\n每次殺不死你殺不死你也醫好你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n切記要爭口氣要爭口氣你不要死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"1484a6ee1c49a3ca3bbe54f90edf3cb25c1588e7","tid":1350040,"uid":48912,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T12:41:52.000Z","msg":"只待燒山一句"},{"pid":"e3c601ccf0895990ed21137427befac91c72fa70","tid":1350040,"uid":96371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T12:41:55.000Z","msg":"是但啦, 上環緊要D呀!!!"},{"pid":"ef18215adcda4454509517488b2bce01a5e18d13","tid":1350040,"uid":188411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T12:42:00.000Z","msg":"佢死唔死冇關係，打到人阿嫂就唔係咁算<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8eb4077644fff901d5e500855f39f2660602548d","tid":1350040,"uid":22689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T12:43:11.000Z","msg":"以為佢死左"},{"pid":"1a7035dd8d47c6859bee23e467d3d044cd2d7d36","tid":1350040,"uid":284452,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T12:44:08.000Z","msg":"死左成日都未死得去，重不停翻生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最好植物人長命百歲啦"},{"pid":"fb6d77132fc15f0379f9f8cd44ef85cb00e7e62a","tid":1350040,"uid":201206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T12:44:11.000Z","msg":"飛天南你要對得住我Id<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbd10250474aa92a4513b02f504621f9ca3154d1","tid":1350040,"uid":277263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T12:44:59.000Z","msg":"多行不義必自斃"},{"pid":"9e68fa5d9211f86e73366e6b86def229156ab543","tid":1350040,"uid":265192,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T12:45:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2x7DQUV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2x7DQUV.png&h=791635de&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家好清楚我地武力升級有限，啲狗仲有好多武器未出，包括實彈同水炮車，呢啲傷害力好高，足以打散我地陣勢<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">硬撼對我地係絕對不利</span><br />\n<br />\n遍地開花是有用的，最緊要係打<span style=\"color: red;\">消耗戰</span><br />\n<br />\n警察只有3萬個，佢地冇可能短時間補充到（除非佢地搵國安扮警察，但係數量唔會多，因為好難落命令同埋組織戰術）<br />\n<br />\n而家夏天佢地下下都出曬防暴裝，朝早企到夜，對佢地身心都造成好大負荷，相反我地可以休息，可以補給，人數多到可以輪住做<br />\n<br />\n我地一定要拎住個<span style=\"color: red;\">主導權</span><br />\n<br />\n1. Be water，唔好戀戰<br />\n<br />\n呢個講咗好耐，但而家唔係講緊執生咁簡單，而係要變成主動一方，撚狗式遊走。<br />\n<br />\n我地逼佢地動員，但唔好引佢地升級武力。喺清場之前我地可以好似以前咁挑釁。<span style=\"color: red;\">當我地逼到佢地要清場嘅時候，我地就要毫不猶豫即刻散</span>，唔好戀戰。<span style=\"color: red;\">可以轉換場地，等佢地重新佈防，又或者留力去第二日</span><br />\n<br />\n總之我地<span style=\"color: red;\">唔好畀時間佢地休息</span>，雖然我地都會有體力消耗，但同佢地比我地會消耗得慢好多<br />\n<br />\n如果啲狗好似七一咁突然走曬去休息呢？我地就唔好畀機會佢地休息<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />即刻升級，逼曬佢地翻出嚟之後又走，令佢地keep住精神繃緊<br />\n<br />\n2. 單一焦點，唔好浪費彈藥<br />\n<br />\n每一次行動都應該事先傾好，制定一個明確嘅目標。<span style=\"color: red;\">當是日目標達成之後，唔好即日觸發第二個事件</span>！好似琴日咁，噴黑國徽同臨時立法會宣言相衝，喺港島嘅焦點就去曬國徽度，我地又浪費咗一粒彈藥。"},{"pid":"6c4775a7a35a5d9a34d20613d6925f40d9e0a455","tid":1350040,"uid":55627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T12:49:59.000Z","msg":"聽聞做左PCI 未死得<br />\n都係睇連登講"},{"pid":"f261703e5cd1fe116af425551fd15e1f7efbdf0d","tid":1350040,"uid":11788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T12:50:18.000Z","msg":"點會俾你咁快死 等你好返做第二個上海仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df4aa38ecdafedd3243029e0f148543b08493cf7","tid":1350040,"uid":62770,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T12:54:40.000Z","msg":"做咩成日叫錯名架<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">佢叫升天南呀</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Z85Fkk8.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZ85Fkk8.gif&h=8744205a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce8a67e1d3aab2109d7fd02f8d2128a80129a069","tid":1350040,"uid":71140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T12:59:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}